EXAMPLE
=======

This example moves seen mails older than one week to alternative
storage under /nfsmount:

.. parsed-literal::

   mail_location = mdbox:~/mdbox:ALT=/nfsmount/%h/mdbox

.. parsed-literal::

   **doveadm altmove -u johnd@example.com seen savedbefore 1w**

